references.paper_title: High-resolution image synthesis with latent diffusion models
references.reason: This paper introduces latent diffusion models, enabling high-resolution image synthesis which the NullFace approach leverages for face anonymization, as the Stable Diffusion model used in this paper is the one adopted in the NullFace technique.

references.paper_title: A style-based generator architecture for generative adversarial networks
references.reason: This paper describes StyleGAN, which is used in some baseline methods the paper is comparing with.

references.paper_title: Prompt-to-prompt image editing with cross attention control
references.reason: This paper describes Prompt-to-Prompt editing which is adapted in this work to modify facial features while maintaining the original image's fidelity.

references.paper_title: Arcface: Additive angular margin loss for deep face recognition
references.reason: This paper introduces ArcFace, a face recognition model that the current work uses to extract face embeddings.
